title: dino crisis (psx.ps1.playstation) velcro113
description:
well... fifth game upload happens to be the first ps1 game i ever owned.
made by capcom, so it is alot like resident evil.
you shoot dinosaurs instead of zombies, has a lot of puzzles, 3 endings, and a lot of secrets(if you can find 'em)
just beware of big ass lizards =]


no story as to why i decided to upload this, i just kinda felt like it.
after all, sharing is caring!(i lub you guys >.<)

my epsxe 1.6 video settings, looks decent(might want to take scanlines off though)
please note that this works good for my comp, might not for yours though. it depends on hardware(for those who didnt know):
